                                    oc:templateContent """## INVOICE

**Invoice Number:** INV-{YYYY}{MM}-{####}
**Date:** {issue_date}
**Due Date:** {due_date}

### Bill To:
{customer_name}
{customer_address}
{customer_email}

### Items:
| Description | Qty | Unit Price | Amount |
|-------------|-----|------------|--------|
| {item_1}    | {q} | ${price}   | ${amt} |
| {item_2}    | {q} | ${price}   | ${amt} |

**Subtotal:** ${subtotal}
**Tax ({tax_rate}%):** ${tax_amount}
**Total Due:** ${total}

### Payment Methods:
- Bank Transfer: {bank_details}
- Credit Card: {payment_link}
- PayPal: {paypal_email}
""" ;
